  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your blood flow slows and heartbeat grows erratic without significant harm to you, increasing your ability to survive freezing temperatures and electric shocks.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Death sphere.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You gain +1 spell point. You can spend a spell point as an immediate action to gain cold resistance 5 and electricity resistance 5 for 1 round. For each necrosis feat you possess beyond this one, the cold and electricity resistances increase by 5 and the duration increases by 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Four Necrosis Feats:</strong> You always have cold resistance 10 and electricity resistance 10, and when you spend a spell point, you gain immunity to cold and electricity for a number of rounds equal to the number of necrosis feats you possess.</p>\n",
